content.text: Substitution, Marseille. Lucas Ocampos replaces Florian Thauvin.
First Half ends, Marseille 3, RB Leipzig 1.
Attempt missed. Kostas Mitroglou (Marseille) right footed shot from the centre of the box is just a bit too high. Assisted by Hiroki Sakai with a cross following a fast break.
Corner,  RB Leipzig. Conceded by Luiz Gustavo.
Kostas Mitroglou (Marseille) wins a free kick in the defensive half.
Attempt missed. Jordan Amavi (Marseille) header from the centre of the box misses to the left. Assisted by Maxime Lopez with a cross.
Corner,  RB Leipzig. Conceded by Boubacar Kamara.
Attempt saved. Kostas Mitroglou (Marseille) left footed shot from very close range is saved in the centre of the goal. Assisted by Boubacar Kamara.
Attempt missed. Boubacar Kamara (Marseille) header from the centre of the box misses to the left. Assisted by Dimitri Payet with a cross following a corner.
Corner,  Marseille. Conceded by Dayotchanculle Upamecano.
Dimitri Payet (Marseille) wins a free kick in the defensive half.
Attempt missed. Dimitri Payet (Marseille) right footed shot from the right side of the box misses to the right. Assisted by Bouna Sarr with a cross.
Lineups are announced and players are warming up.
